{ «Steigerung von Adjektiven

  table { ll
    angry ☰ furious
    beutiful ☰ gorgeous
    big ☰ massive
    boring ☰ dull
    noisy ☰ deafening
    poor ☰ destitute
    creative ☰ innovative
    crowded ☰ bustling
    dear ☰ cherished
    deep ☰ profound
    empty ☰ desolate
    exited ☰ thrilled
    fancy ☰ lavish
    fat ☰ obese
    friendly ☰ amiable
    glad ☰ overjoyed
    great ☰ terrific
    heavy ☰ leaden (dated?)
    calm ☰ serene
    ugly ☰ hideous
    small ☰ petite
    funny ☰ hilarious
    quiet ☰ hushed
    rich ☰ wealthy
    accurate ☰ exact
    afraid ☰ fearful
    clever ☰ intelligent
    cute ☰ adorable
    dull ☰ tedious (?)
    eager ☰ keen
    evil ☰ wicked
    fierce ☰ ferocious
    light ☰ luminous
    lively ☰ animated
    lovely ☰ adorable
rem {
    fast ☰ quick
rem }

  table }

